<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288038>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Litho- and biostratigraphy of the observed parts of the Reuchenette Formation in the Ajoie, with distribution of oysters and characteristic fossils. A. Synthetic section. B. Detailed section of the Banné Member in Vâ Tche Tchâ (VTT), Lower Kimmeridgian. C. Detailed section of the upper part of the Courtedoux Member and “ Lower Virgula Marl ”; based on Tchâfouè (TCH) and Sur Combe Ronde (SCR), Upper Kimmeridgian (note separate bed numeration for VTT and SCR / TCH)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288038/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

